<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>some.pics (中文)</title><link>https://some.pics</link><description>只是网上的一些图片。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Fri, 22 May 2026 20:49:11 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a10c1441e445</link><description>&lt;p&gt;我不知道你为何说再见，我却说你好。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A photo of a TV, paused on a frame showing Paul McCartney and Steven Colbert. Paul is flipping a large electrical box switch to off, near the final moments of the final episode of The Late Show with Stephen Colbert. There are visual fx fake sparks coming from the switch, and Stephen has a contemplative half-smile on his face. You can see the entertainment center shelf with photo frames and other items displayed below the TV. " height="2268" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/duggan/6a10c1441e445.jpg" width="4032"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://duggan.some.pics"&gt;@duggan&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 May 2026 20:49:11 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a106e30e27c6</link><description>&lt;p&gt;下班后的闲暇时光&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A b&amp;amp;w picture of a tricycle parked in a corner." height="3808" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/roteskuffen/6a106e30e27c6.jpg" width="2856"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://roteskuffen.some.pics"&gt;@roteskuffen&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 May 2026 14:54:44 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a10379f34509</link><description>&lt;p&gt;收藏&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Shards of brown glass, apparently from a bottle, lined up on a concrete surface." height="2000" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/z428/6a10379f34509.jpg" width="1125"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://z428.some.pics"&gt;@z428&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 22